      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$21,500 - Ready for its next journey! This dependable vehicle is in fair condition and has plenty of life left for a driver looking for a solid, functional ride. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a reliable choice that's ready to get you where you need to go with character and spirit!",
